  "detailed_description": "Join the blue haired treasure hunter Fares in the adventure of a lifetime in this retro inspired 16-bit platformer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDiscover hidden treasures and artifacts as you travel through dangerous lands of a lost civilization.  Can you complete Fares collection? See if you can in this colorful and cute adventure!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKey Features:-<br />\r\n   - Stunning Environments<br />\r\n   - Catchy Music<br />\r\n   - Keep track of your treasures<br />\r\n   - Discover the secrets of lost civilizations <br />\r\n   - Classic platforming adventure inspired by the games of the 1990’s<br />\r\n   - See if you can beat the challenging speed run mode and become the greatest and fastest adventurer",
